#. lang="pi"><section class="sutta" id="thag4.10"><article><div
#. class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "thag4.10:1.1"
msgid "Theragāthā"
msgstr "Verses of the Senior Monks"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "thag4.10:2.1"
msgid "Catukkanipāta"
msgstr "The Book of the Fours"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "thag4.10:3.1"
msgid "Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "Chapter One"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag4.10:4.1"
msgid "4.10. Dhammikattheragāthā"
msgstr "4.10. Dhammika"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a>
msgctxt "thag4.10:5.1"
msgid ""
"<span class=\"cross\" title=\"^ne4#1 [Vibhaṅga/ Desanāhāravibhaṅga] | ^ne4#"
"141 [Vibhaṅga/ Catubyūhahāravibhaṅga], ^ne4#198 [Vibhaṅga/ "
"Āvaṭṭahāravibhaṅga] | ^pe2#55 [Sāsanapaṭṭhānadutiyabhūmi]\" id=\"note177\""
">*</span> <a class=\"verse-num-sc\" id=\"verse-num-sc303\"></a><a class"
"=\"verse-num-pts\" id=\"verse-num-pts303\"></a>“Dhammo have rakkhati "
"dhammacāriṃ,"
msgstr "“Dhamma surely protects one who practices Dhamma;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.10:5.2"
msgid "Dhammo suciṇṇo sukhamāvahati;"
msgstr "the teaching brings happiness when practiced well."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.10:5.3"
msgid "Esānisaṃso dhamme suciṇṇe,"
msgstr "This is the benefit of practicing Dhamma:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.10:5.4"
msgid "Na duggatiṃ gacchati dhammacārī."
msgstr "one doesn’t go to a bad destination."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a>
msgctxt "thag4.10:6.1"
msgid ""
"<span class=\"cross\" title=\"^ja510#23 [Ayogharajātaka] | ^ne6#460 "
"[Sāsanapaṭṭhāna]\" id=\"note178\">*</span> <a class=\"verse-num-sc\" id"
"=\"verse-num-sc304\"></a><a class=\"verse-num-pts\" id=\"verse-num-pts304\""
"></a>Na hi dhammo adhammo ca,"
msgstr "It’s not the case that Dhamma and what is not Dhamma"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.10:6.2"
msgid "ubho samavipākino;"
msgstr "lead to the same results."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.10:6.3"
msgid "Adhammo nirayaṃ neti,"
msgstr "What is not Dhamma leads to hell,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.10:6.4"
msgid "dhammo pāpeti suggatiṃ."
msgstr "while Dhamma takes you to a good place."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc305"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts305"></a>
msgctxt "thag4.10:7.1"
msgid "Tasmā hi dhammesu kareyya chandaṃ,"
msgstr "So you should rouse enthusiasm for the teachings;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.10:7.2"
msgid "Iti modamāno sugatena tādinā;"
msgstr "such rejoicing is owing to the Holy One, the poised."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.10:7.3"
msgid "Dhamme ṭhitā sugatavarassa sāvakā,"
msgstr "The disciples of the best of Holy Ones are firm in the teaching;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.10:7.4"
msgid "Nīyanti dhīrā saraṇavaraggagāmino”."
msgstr "those wise ones are led on, headed to the very best of refuges.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc306"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts306"></a>
msgctxt "thag4.10:8.1"
msgid "“Vipphoṭito gaṇḍamūlo,"
msgstr "“The boil has been burst from its root,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.10:8.2"
msgid "Taṇhājālo samūhato;"
msgstr "the net of craving is eradicated."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.10:8.3"
msgid "So khīṇasaṃsāro na catthi kiñcanaṃ,"
msgstr "He has ended transmigration, he has nothing,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag4.10:8.4"
msgid "Cando yathā dosinā puṇṇamāsiyan”ti."
msgstr "he’s like the full moon on a bright night.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "thag4.10:9.1"
msgid "…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "thag4.10:9.2"
msgid "Dhammiko thero …."
msgstr ""
